      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Former Kiwi GREASED LIGHTNIN NZ (4) made a strong start in Queensland when successful at Albion Park last week, getting home by 3.6 metres after racing parked. Goes back 10m in the handicap but is two from two when second-up so should be improved. Can take this next step. COSMIC FLYER (2) has been solid at Albion Park in two outings since winning here, beaten just a head last week. His record at this circuit stands at five wins and three placings from nine attempts and he has the ability to mix it with them. DRAGON (3) added to a string of top-four finishes when third to Greased Lightnin despite breaking early last start at Albion Park. Can't make any mistakes against this field but he is in the mix if he gets it right. JIMARTEE (12) has been below his best of late but does enjoy a significant drop in class.",
